价：\n\n- 需要维护 catalog 和条目成熟度。\n- 需要在归档阶段控制噪音，避免把一次性结论误升为规则。\n\n## Evidence\n\n本条来自 `docs/doc/` 中对 Harness Engineering 和知识沉淀实践的分析，初始成熟度为 `draft`。\n\r\n\n succeeded in 375ms:\n succeeded in 342ms:\n---\nid: GUIDELINE-RULES-001\ntype: guideline\nmaturity: draft\ntags: [rules, governance, context]\napplicable_phases: [analysis, plan, implement, review]\nsource_references:\n  - docs/doc/1.md\nlast_referenced:\ncontributors:\n  - codex\n---\n\n# 规则必须短入口、深文档、可验证\n\n## Context\n\n根规则过长会消耗指令预算，孤立深文档又容易不被发现。当前仓库已经有 `AGENTS.md`、`docs/harness/*`、`.agents/rules/*` 和 `.codex/prompts/*` 多层规则面，需要明确分层。\n\n## Guidance\n\n- `AGENTS.md` 只保留每次会话必须遵守的硬约束和深文档索引。\n- 复杂流程写入 `docs/harness/*` 或 `.agents/rules/*`。\n- 执行时必须注入的行为写入 `.codex/prompts/*`。\n- 禁令必须包含替代方案。\n- 能自动检查的规则应进入脚本、schema 或 hook，而不是只靠文字约束。\n\n## Evidence\n\n本条来自 `docs/doc/1.md` 的规则工程分析，初始成熟度为 `draft`。\n\r\n\n succeeded in 363ms:\n{\r\n    \"runtime\":  {\r\n                    \"driver\":  \"powershell -NoProfile -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File .\\\\codex-loop.ps1\",\r\n                    \"trace_dir\":  \"traces\",\r\n                    \"agent\":  \"codex\",\r\n                    \"run_profile\":  \".codex\\\\task-run-profile.json\",\r\n                    \"git\":  {\r\n                                \"require_clean_workspace\":  true,\r\n                                \"non_blocking_dirty_paths\":  [\r\n                                                                 \"traces/\"\r\n                                                             ]\r\n                            },\r\n                    \"session\":  {\r\n                                    \"mode\":  \"fresh-process\",\r\n                                    \"carry_forward_summary\":  false\r\n                                },\r\n                    \"handoff\":  {\r\n                                    \"feature_id\":  \"FEAT-EXPORT-PLATFORM-001\",\r\n                                    \"truth_sources\":  {\r\n                                             